  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "CHAPTER 11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "2Ch 11:1-17. Rehoboam, Raising an Army to Subdue Israel, Is Forbidden by Shemaiah.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1-4. Rehoboam … gathered of the house of Judah and Benjamin … to fight against Israel—(See 1Ki 12:21-24).Rehoboam raising an army to subdue Israel, is forbidden by Shemaiah, 1 Chronicles 11:1-4. He strengtheneth his kingdom with forts and provision, 2 Chronicles 11:5-12. The priests and Levites, and such as feared God, forsaken by Jeroboam, who turneth idolater, strengthen the kingdom of Judah, 2 Chronicles 11:13-17. The wives and children of Rehoboam, 2 Chronicles 11:18-23.  Of this verse, and verses 2-4, See Poole \"1 Kings 12:21\". ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "1-4. Rehoboam … gathered of the house of Judah and Benjamin … to fight against Israel—(See 1Ki 12:21-24).Rehoboam raising an army to subdue Israel, is forbidden by Shemaiah, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "1 Chronicles 11:1-4",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". He strengtheneth his kingdom with forts and provision, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 11:5-12",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". The priests and Levites, and such as feared God, forsaken by Jeroboam, who turneth idolater, strengthen the kingdom of Judah, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 11:13-17",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". The wives and children of Rehoboam, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 11:18-23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "p",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " Of this verse, and verses 2-4, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "See Poole \"1 Kings 12:21\"",
            "children": []
          },
          {
