      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(a) That is, the half tribe of Benjamin for the other half went after Jeroboam.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(b) Meaning the ten tribes who rebelled.",
        "children": []
      }
